snippet.title: First Strike: MULTIPLAYER｜Official Trailer (EN)
snippet.description:
Finally, you can nuke your friends!
The most requested feature for First Strike is happening! First Strike Multiplayer is finally here! Unleash Armageddon alone OR annihilate everyone in MULTIPLAYER.
The Multiplayer Update is available for the free mobile version of First Strike on Android and iOS.

Ready to wage nuclear war against your friends?
First Strike on the Apple App Store: https://apps.apple.com/app/apple-store/id1434281598?mt=8

First Strike on the Google Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.blindflugstudios.firststrike.free&hl

FIRST STRIKE HOMEPAGE: http://www.firststrike.mobi/
